*testdisk-6.3 (25 May 2006)

  25 May 2006; Robin H. Johnson <robbat2@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  +testdisk-6.3.ebuild:
  Bug #128489, version bump. Also fix broken NTFS and reiserfs support - this
  last actually worked in the 5.7 ebuild, and has been broken badly since.

  11 Nov 2005; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org> testdisk-5.9.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc.

  07 Nov 2005; Daniel Black <dragonheart@gentoo.org> testdisk-5.9.ebuild,
  testdisk-6.2.ebuild:
  changed sys-fs/progsreiserfs dependancy to sys-fs/reiserfsprogs thanks to
  Chris Gianellonis suggestion in bug #84514. Made version 5.9 x86 stable

*testdisk-6.2 (07 Nov 2005)

  07 Nov 2005; Daniel Black <dragonheart@gentoo.org> testdisk-5.2.ebuild,
