*testdisk-5.7 (30 Apr 2005)

  30 Apr 2005; Daniel Black <dragonheart@gentoo.org> testdisk-5.2.ebuild,
  -testdisk-5.3.ebuild, -testdisk-5.5.ebuild, testdisk-5.6.ebuild,
  +testdisk-5.7.ebuild:
  Version bump. better descriptions added. old versions removed. added
  reiserfs USE flag to include/exclude a reiserfs libs as per bug
  #84514 by Alexey Maximov <amax@mail.ru>.

